'''氢化铝'''（AlH<sub>3</sub>）是[[铝|铝]]的[[氢化物|氢化物]]。用作[[还原剂|还原剂]]。用于[[炔烃|炔烃]]的[[铝氢化反应|铝氢化反应]]、[[烯丙重排反应|烯丙重排反应]]以及[[氢燃料汽车|氢燃料汽车]]中氢气的储存。<ref name = galatsis>Galatsis, P. In ''Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis''; University of Guelph, Ontario, Canada</ref><ref>Brown, H. C.; Krishnamurthy, S. ''[[Tetrahedron_(journal)|Tetrahedron]]'' '''1979''', ''35'', 567. (Review)</ref>

氢化铝是无色的聚合结构固体（(AlH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>n</sub>）。

==历史==
氢化铝最早是以杂质或胺／醚络合物的形式得到。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = F. M. Brower, N. E. Matzek, P. F. Reigler, H. W. Rinn, C. B. Roberts, D. L. Schmidt, J. A. Snover, K. Terada | publisher = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1976 | volume = 98 | pages = 2450–2454 | doi = 10.1021/ja00425a011 | title = Preparation and properties of aluminum hydride | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society}}</ref>直到1947年，芝加哥大学的 Finholt 等才首次制得纯的氢化铝。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = A. E. Finholt, A. C. Bond, Jr., H. I. Schlesinger | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]] | year = 1947 | volume = 69 | pages = 1199–1203 | doi = 10.1021/ja01197a061 | title = Lithium Aluminum Hydride, Aluminum Hydride and Lithium Gallium Hydride, and Some of their Applications in Organic and Inorganic Chemistry}}</ref>

==结构与物理性质==
氢化铝有多种晶型，较为常见的有 α-、α'-、β-、δ-、ε-、θ- 和 γ-型。α-氢化铝为立方或菱方结构，每个 Al 原子被6个 H 原子包围，每个 H 原子再各自与另外一个 Al 原子桥连；Al-H 键长均为 172 pm，Al-H-Al 角为 141°。<ref>{{cite journal en| title = The crystal structure of aluminum hydride| author =Turley J W,. Rinn H W  | journal = Inorganic Chemistry| year = 1969 | volume = 8 | issue = 1 | pages = 18–22 | doi = 10.1021/ic50071a005 }}</ref>α'-型氢化铝则为针状结晶。

氢化铝可溶于[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]和醚。

