===氢化铝分子===
{{see also|乙铝烷}}
AlH<sub>3</sub>单体已在低温的固体[[惰性气体|惰性气体]]基质中分离，结构为平面型分子，很不稳定。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Molecular Aluminium Trihydride, AlH<sub>3</sub>: Generation in a Solid Noble Gas Matrix and Characterisation by its Infrared Spectrum and ''ab initio'' Calculations |author1=Kurth, F. A. |author2=Eberlein, R. A. |author3=Schnöckel, H.-G. |author4=Downs, A. J. |author5=Pulham, C. R. | journal = Journal of the Chemical Society, Chemical Communications | year = 1993 | volume = 1993 | issue = 16 | pages = 1302–1304 | doi = 10.1039/C39930001302 }}</ref>它的二聚体[[乙铝烷|Al<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub>]]已在固态氢中分离。它的结构和[[乙硼烷|乙硼烷]]（B<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub>）以及[[乙镓烷|乙镓烷]]（Ga<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub>）一样。<ref>{{cite journal | title = The Infrared Spectrum of Al<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub> in Solid Hydrogen |author1=Andrews, L. |author2=Wang, X. | journal = Science | year = 2003 | volume = 299 | issue = 5615 | pages = 2049–2052 | doi = 10.1126/science.1082456 | pmid = 12663923 |bibcode = 2003Sci...299.2049A |s2cid=45856199 }}</ref><ref name = "Pulham">{{cite journal | title = Gallane: Synthesis, Physical and Chemical Properties, and Structure of the Gaseous Molecule Ga<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub> as Determined by Electron Diffraction |author1=Pulham, C. R. |author2=Downs, A. J. |author3=Goode, M. J. |author4=Rankin D. W. H. |author5=Robertson, H. E. | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society | year = 1991 | volume = 113 | issue = 14 | pages = 5149–5162 | doi = 10.1021/ja00014a003 }}</ref>

==化学性质==
α-氢化铝为热稳定性最高的晶型。

β- 和 γ-型氢化铝通常会共同生成，并且在加热时会转变为 α-氢化铝。δ-、ε- 和 θ-氢化铝则在不同的结晶条件下生成；虽然其稳定性不及 α-变体，但加热时并不会发生晶型转变。<ref name = lund>Lund, Gary K., Hanks, Jami M., Johnston, Harold E., US Patent and Trade Office, '''2007''', Pat. Application # 20070066839</ref>

AlH<sub>3</sub> 可与强[[路易斯碱|路易斯碱]]很快形成加合物。例如它可与[[三甲胺|三甲胺]]形成 1:1 和 1:2 两种加合物。1:1加合物在气相是四面体型结构，<ref name = "greenwood"> {{Greenwood&Earnshaw}}</ref>在固态则为含有氢桥的二聚结构——(NMe<sub>3</sub>Al(μ-H))<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal en
